quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  26,184,"Ne rie owabaloonga enywe nende ebiloonje biabura bioosi.""
  26,185,"Baboola mbu: “Toto ewe oli mubalia abalokwa."
  26,186,"Newe sholi shiosishiosi tawe halali omundu sa shinga efwe, ne toto efwe khukhulola mbu oli mubabeyi."
  26,187,"Kho mana khukwisilie ebitonye bia likulu toto noli mubalia baboolanga obwatieli.”"
  26,188,"Naboola mbu: “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi amanyile muno akamukholanga.”"
  26,189,"Mana nibamuyingasia, ne eshinyasio shieyinyanga yeshinikha nishiboolela. Toto esho shali eshinyasio shieyinyanga ikhongo."
  26,190,"Toto mu ako kalimwo ameeko, halali abanji mubo shibali bokhusuubila tawe."
  26,191,"Ne toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi niye Owamaani, Owetsimbabaasi muno."
  26,192,"Ne toto obo ni obwishio bwa Nyasaye Omulesi webiloonje bioosi."
  26,193,"Yekha nabwo Roho omwisikwa."
  26,194,"Khu mwoyo kukwo, kho obe mubalia abekanyilisinjia."
  26,195,"Mulusungo lwa olwarabu lwa habulafu."
  26,196,"Ne toto kano kali mubitabu ebiaranjilila."
  26,197,"Koo, shishiali eshimanyisio khubo tawe mbu kano bakamanya abasomi ba Abana ba Israili?"
  26,198,"Ne khushishinjia khu ulia ulali omwarabu tawe."
  26,199,"Mana abasoomele, shibakhamusuubile tawe."
  26,200,"Ne endi nilwa khwinjisinjia (okhukatsula) mumioyo chia ababii."
  26,201,"Shibayisuubilanga tawe okhula shingala balola eshinyasio eshilulu."
  26,202,"Mana shibetsele mapwoka, nabo nibalamanyile tawe."
  26,203,"Mana baboole mbu: “Koo, efwe khulahebwa ebise?”"
  26,204,"Mana koo, bayungubalilanga eshinyasio shiefu?"
  26,205,"Olola orie nikhubamenyia obulayi emika eminji."
  26,206,"Mana kabanyoole kalia akabalakungwa."